room_title: Escape room "1920’s Lancaster Train Station" by Escape Room Lancaster in Lancaster
review: We went with a group and had a wonderful time.  It is an action packed hour.  I would highly recommend for a family or group.

room_title: Escape room "1920’s Lancaster Train Station" by Escape Room Lancaster in Lancaster
review: Only done one room so far but it was a lot of fun. Staff was friendly and helpful. Escaped the train room with only six minutes to spare.
